# Site UI (src/)

Custom React code for the Docusaurus site — homepage, components, and global styles.

## Conventions

- Functional components (see `src/pages/index.js`, `src/components/HomepageFeatures/`)
- CSS modules colocated with components (`*.module.css`)
- Global theme overrides in `src/css/custom.css`

## When editing

- Match existing import and component patterns.
- Run `pnpm typecheck` and `pnpm build` after changes.
- Static assets belong in `static/img/`, not `src/`.
